<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4757679>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 1-4. Sierracapnia barberi. Male: 1. North Fork Cosumnes River, California. Genitalia, dorsal, epiproct. 2. North Fork Cosumnes River, California. Genitalia, lateral, epiproct and knob on tergum 7. 3. Sierra Canyon Creek, Nevada. Knob on tergum 7, dorsal, anterior. 4. Sierra Canyon Creek, Nevada. Tip of paraprocts and fusion plate (center prong), ventral, terminal." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4757679/files/figure.png" .

